{
  "stem": "7069.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But finally, then we managed by buying off-- now I'm telling you that I was a criminal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By buying off a Berlin official who would fake this head exchange for a few hundred dollars-- for a few hundred marks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did that although we didn't have much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just had barely saved that much together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I came out of the concentration camp with my striped clothes, practically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nothing, no money, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we-- did the-- we paid this man off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that way we were allowed with falsified papers to move into the English sector of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, we were there in that English sector finally maybe four or five weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then the French, by that time, allowed everybody to move out the way they wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyways, we have no bad feelings about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So therefore, we arrive now in America, in New York with the ship.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got nicely seasick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Worse, apparently, than my wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Although she was seasick, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had our little daughter there with us, who was one year old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't think she noticed anything of that ride.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we arrived in New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, New York, as we knew, is a melting pot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were earmarked to go to St.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Paul.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, the reason for that was we came-- we were supported by an organization, the-- the-- the-- [INAUDIBLE], I believe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The American Joint Contribution.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Joint-- I can't think of it right now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Joint-- well, anyways, maybe I can later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, they would pay everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would pay the fare.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would guarantee for a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And would also guarantee for five years for our being five years in America until we became citizens.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
